'''Teklet''' was a city on [[Qiilura/Legends|Qiilura]] that had a major communications facility. During [[Omega Squad]]'s mission, [[Niner Skirata|Niner]] drove an explosive-rigged mining droid into the communications facility before Omega Squad attacked the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] research facility.

==Appearances==
*''[[Star Wars: Republic Commando]]'' {{Mo}}
*''[[Republic Commando: Hard Contact]]'' {{1st}}
